    "body": "As mentioned here (https://github.com/mason-org/mason-registry/pull/6330#issuecomment-3971724747), there is a change (https://github.com/dotnet/roslyn/pull/82201/changes) that the official language server can be easily installed via `dotnet` cli.\r\n\r\nThis change uses it's binary name per default.",
